name: IC-001 Extractor
description: This device is used to extractExoticsfrom Exotic Deposits. It requires theIC-001 Prototype Power Sourceto operate and can extract approximately 330 exotics per power source. The speed of the IC-001 Extractor is the same as theElectric Extractor. Due to a bug, the IC-001 Extractor will operate at the same speed as theBiofuel Extractor.
